CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `download_events` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `downloadId` int NOT NULL,
  `ipHash` varchar(64),
  `userAgent` varchar(512),
  `referer` varchar(512),
  `country` varchar(8),
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `download_events_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `idx_download_events_downloadId` (`downloadId`),
  INDEX `idx_download_events_createdAt` (`createdAt`)
);

ALTER TABLE `downloads` ADD COLUMN `downloadCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0;
